mea: ʻO kēlā me kēia mea e lawe i ka lewa a loaʻa ka nuipa
\u02bb\u0101toma: ʻĀpana liʻiliʻi loa o ka mea hiki ke komo i loko o ka hopena kemika
mole mole: Pūʻulu ʻelua a ʻoi aku paha nā ʻātoma i hoʻopaʻa ʻia
\u02bbele\u02bbele: ʻO ka mea maʻemaʻe i hana ʻia me hoʻokahi ʻano atom
p\u016bhui: Mea i hana ʻia me ʻelua mau mea ʻokoʻa like ʻole i hoʻopaʻa ʻia
k\u016blana o ka mea: ʻO ke ʻano i loaʻa kahi mea (paʻa, wai, kinoea, plasma)
umekaumaha: ʻO ka ikaika e huki ai i nā mea me ka nuipaʻa i kekahi i kekahi
magnetism: ʻO ka ikaika i hana ʻia e nā magnet ma kekahi mau mea
ikaika: Paʻi a huki paha e hiki ai i kekahi mea ke hoʻokē a hoʻololi i ke ala
\u02bboni: Hoʻololi i ke kūlana o kahi mea i ka manawa
ka wikiwiki: Ka māmā holo a me ke kuhikuhi o kekahi mea
m\u0101m\u0101: ʻO ke ʻano o ka ikehu e holo ana ma ke ʻano he nalu
kani: Ke ʻano o ka ikehu e holo ana ma ke ʻano he hawewe ma waena o kahi ʻano
wela: Ka hoʻololi ʻana o ka ikehu wela mai kahi mea mahana a i kahi mea ʻoluʻolu
mahana wela: Ana i ka wela a me ke anu o kekahi mea
ka makani: Nā kūlana o ka lewa i kahi manawa a me kahi kikoʻī
ke ea: ʻO ke ʻano o ke aniau ma kahi kikoʻī no ka wā lōʻihi
kaiaolaola: Ke kaiaulu o nā mea ola e launa pū ana me kekahi a me ko lākou wahi ola ʻole
heluna kanaka: Hui o na mea ola o ka ano like e noho ana ma kekahi wahi
ho\u02bbomohala \u02bbana: Ke kaʻina hana e loli ai ka nui o nā mea ola i ka manawa
\u02bb\u014dnaehana l\u0101: ʻO ka lā a me nā mea i hoʻopaʻa ʻia me ia
galaxy: ʻOhi nui o nā hōkū, kinoea, a me ka lepo
ke ao holo\u02bboko\u02bba: ʻO nā mea a pau, e like me ka mea, ka ikehu, ka lewa, a me ka manawa
